---
title: Grilled Mediterranean Double Salmon with Creamy Orzo and Feta Salad
description: Orzo salad with spinach, tomatoes and yogurt sauce is paired with spiced, grilled salmon for big flavours inspired by the sunny Mediterranean coast!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-saumon-grille-a-la-mediterraneenne-5beb6bf5.jpg
